# OKDR Review Site

Static review mockups for the proposed unified OKDR (Okinawa Kobudo Doushi Rensei-Kai) + Authentic Ancient Arts website redesign. Three self-contained HTML files deployed to DigitalOcean App Platform via GitHub. This is a stakeholder review site — not the production Flask app.

## Files

- `index.html` — OKDR home page (kobudo HQ framing, AAA dojo as honbu)
- `karate.html` — Shorin-Ryu Shorinkan karate detail page
- `kobudo.html` — Matayoshi kobudo detail page (the organization's primary art)
- `dojos.html` — full worldwide member dojo directory (from okdr.org/affiliates)
- All pages cross-link via nav, breadcrumb, and footer
- The OKDR crest uses `okdr-black-bg.png` (black background, gold emblem) — referenced from all pages

## Hard constraints

- Static HTML only. No build step. No package.json. No framework.
- Do not extract CSS into separate files. Each HTML page is intentionally self-contained.
- Do not restructure, refactor, or "improve" the design. It has been iteratively approved by the user and stakeholders.
- Do not add dependencies or tooling beyond what is needed for deploy.
- Do not extend this toward the production Flask/Jinja2 app — that comes later.
- Python only for any scripting or tooling (per user's stack preference).

## Key facts (verify before editing related content)

- OKDR founded January 2002 by Gakiya Yoshiaki Sensei
- Kobudo lineage: Matayoshi Shinpo (d. 1997) → Gakiya Yoshiaki → Neil Stolsmark (President since 2011)
- Hanshi Stolsmark: 9th Dan Kobudo, 8th Dan Karate
- Karate lineage: Chibana → Shugoro Nakazato → Minoru Nakazato → Stolsmark
- Honbu = Authentic Ancient Arts, 369 W Main St, Waukesha, WI 53186

## Design and content conventions

- Preserve gold (kobudo) / red (karate) color coding throughout.
- After any filename or link change, verify cross-page links still work (`index.html` ↔ `karate.html` ↔ `kobudo.html` ↔ `dojos.html`).
- Link targets use `index.html`, `karate.html`, `kobudo.html`, `dojos.html`, and anchor hashes (e.g. `index.html#honbu`) — not old names like `OKDR-mockup.html`.
- Honor Gakiya Sensei in any kobudo content.

## Deployment

- Push to `main` on GitHub; DO App Platform auto-deploys as a static site (~30s).
- No build command. Output directory is `/`. Index document is `index.html`.

## Pending content questions for Sensei

- Karate kata curriculum on karate.html — verify the kata list matches Shorinkan progression
- Class schedule placeholders need real times
- Madison Shibu (Don & Theresa Wideman) — should be added to the home page member dojos section?
- Affiliated dojos — the 4 shown are a curated selection; Sensei may want a different mix featured

## When making edits

- Keep changes minimal and scoped to what was requested.
- Edit HTML directly; commit and push when the user asks.
- Keep it boring. Boring deploys reliably.
